The program entered Phase 6.5 First Production on 6 March 2024. The first flight test was performed in FY 2019, the second flight test was performed in FY 2020, the
third in FY 2022, and the final flight test was completed on 4 June 2024. The program was approved to enter Full Rate Production on 21 November 2024. The program
is tailored to use the Joint Department of Defense - Department of Energy Phase 6.x processes for routine nuclear stockpile activities to align with USN and DOE/NNSA
operations. The next phase will be 6.6 Full Scale Production. Program plans to enter Phase 6.6 during 3QFY2025.

