planned to be accomplished in FY 2025 under the Integrated Combat Effects (ICE) Vanguard Pathfinder captured in the FY 2025
PB. This effort matured sufficiently in FY 2024 to graduate into its own thrust, labeled Swift Hammer. The scope related to Swift
Hammer was moved from the ICE Pathfinder into the Swift Hammer Vanguard Prospect.

