D. Acquisition Strategy
The Air Force is lead service for the T-6 Operational Systems Development program and currently manages upgrades to the entire family of systems for both the
Air Force and Navy. T-6 Operational Systems Development acquisition strategy for satisfying emerging software and hardware requirements is designed to enable
