weapon systems.

FY 2026 Plans:
- Transitioning work under project 642812, Acquisition/System Security Engineering, and continue managing and analyzing data
from annual FY21 NDAA 1712 Strategic Cybersecurity Program (SCP) and FY24 NDAA 1502 cyber data call and to understand
the DAF's cyber vulnerability and mitigation landscape and inform SECAF investment priorities.
