Title: B-2 Advanced Communications -- Adaptable Communications Suite (ACS) 4.0                                                            23.719        5.517         0.000
Description: ACS 4.0 provides secure beyond line-of-sight SATCOM Command and Control connectivity. ACS 4.0 will involve
replacing the current radios and ancillaries to transition B-2 SATCOM to Mobile User Objective System due to the sunset of
the current Ultra High Frequency Follow-On satellite constellation. Along with the aircraft system, the ACS ground systems and
