of nuclear play in four Service, four Combatant Command, two Joint Staff, two U.S. Forces Korea, and four Five Eyes /NATO
wargames and exercises.
-Complete impact analysis of proliferated Mid-Earth Orbit and Geostationary Earth Orbit satellites nuclear survivability on
conventional nuclear integration operations.
-Complete scintillation study in support of nuclear survivability analysis request for Army and combatant commands' (U.S. Space
Command, U.S. Strategic Command, and U.S. European Command) Operational Planning.
- Complete persistent nuclear effects survivability study in support of Space Development Agency and U.S. Space Force requests.

