Description: The MATH program ensures the sustainment of the MM III weapons system and concurrent transition to Sentinel
without any disruption to the nuclear deterrence mission. The current transportation and handling (T&H) equipment will not sustain
MM III through end of life. The current T&H TDP is out of date; several items have obsolescence issues. Engineering is needed to
provide adequate and complete technical data to support acquisition of MM III T&H equipment. Items include the following:

a. Propulsion System Rocket Engine (PSRE) semi-trailer (PST);
b. PSRE tractor;
c. Rocket Motor semi-trailer (RMS);
d. Support Equipment (SE).

