- Complete five site visits to ensure compatibility with legacy HACTS (1.0) to inform design of next generation (2.0)
- Begin assembly of 2 EMD units (without EMD circuit card assemblies)
- Generate Software Development Test (SDT) and Systems Integration Test (SIT) test plans and procedures
